    <item>
      <title>Dark Theme</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/features/dark-mode/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/features/dark-mode/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You can change the current theme between dark and light mode by using the switcher icon at the right of the navbar.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The colors tweaked by the theme change are ideally defined in a non bundled CSS file (to optimize caching, since the theming is expected to change more than the rest) under the &lt;code&gt;:root[color-scheme^=&#39;dark/light&#39;]&lt;/code&gt; selector. Should you want to adjust them, a simple stylesheet rules override should suffice. You can read about it in &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/features/customization&#34;&gt;customization&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Static Content</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/features/static-content/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/features/static-content/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Some of the static content on the site, like the home greetings and side pane content, can be defined in the file at &lt;code&gt;data/rtwt/content.yaml&lt;/code&gt;. The structure to do so is as follows:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Note: It&amp;rsquo;s possible to use file formats other than YAML, but the key structure must remain the same!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;home&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;image&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;images/greetings.jpg&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;greetings&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;A Hugo Theme for Bloggers!&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;text&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;The definitive, configurable, customizable, old fashioned rusty coloured theme for web writers and readers.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;side&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;home&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  - &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;content&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Oh, and did I mention it has support for static side pane content? Cool, right?&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  - &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Media Support&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;content&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Side content can have images!&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;imagePath&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;images/hugo.svg&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;imageHref&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;https://gohugo.io&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;imageWidth&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;100%&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Didn&amp;rsquo;t find a value you&amp;rsquo;re looking for? Check the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/math-queiroz/rusty-typewriter&#34;&gt;repository&lt;/a&gt; for the given file (which may be updated with it), or create a new feature request!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Taxonomies Support</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/features/taxonomies-support/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/features/taxonomies-support/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The main taxonomy in the theme is &lt;code&gt;tags&lt;/code&gt;, as it is the one listed under the title in every &amp;ldquo;single&amp;rdquo; page, but it&amp;rsquo;s also possible to set any number of arbitrary taxonomies which will be listed in the side pane details section.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;For example, in this site there&amp;rsquo;s the taxonomies &lt;code&gt;topic&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;series&lt;/code&gt; as defined in the config file.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;taxonomies&lt;/span&gt;]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;tag&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;tags&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;topic&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;topics&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;series&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;series&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
